episodes.title: Liberal MP’s Sister Exposes Father’s Church as Cult with Gay Conversion Fears
episodes.description:
Daughter of City Builders pastor voices grave concerns to Victorian parliamentary inquiry, alleging ongoing cult practices and potential gay conversion therapy within the church founded by her father.
